des:
AO Smith Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your Geyser.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your Geyser - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Geyser products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "AO Smith Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "AO Smith Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some AO Smith Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "AO Smith Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "AO Smith Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "AO Smith Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "AO Smith Smart", and you'll be navigated to "AO Smith Smart" login page;
(9). Input your AO Smith Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the Geyser”
"Alexa, turn off the Geyser"
"Alexa, set the Geyser to 80 degrees"
"Alexa, increase the Geyser temperature"
"Alexa, decrease the Geyser temperature"
"Alexa, what's the temperature of the Geyser"
